Trevor Noah's live show "There's a Gupta on my stoep" tickets almost sold out&nbsp; Trevor Noah is known for his intelligent sense of humour and this time he is bringing his best to the table. The tickets of the show "There's a Zulu on my stoep" are selling like hot cakes. The show will take place from the 9th to 12th of August at the Dome in Johannesburg. Trevor never disappoints. The tickets will be sold at R450 pp. &nbsp;For more prices check out his website. Tickets are sold online or at computicket. Only people with an intelligent sense of humour will enjoy and the rest should continue watching Rhtym city.